FT  18 NOV 94 / Saudis due to start Gulf payments
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   DUBAI
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Saudi Arabia will next week pay back part of a Dollars 4.5bn sovereign loan
it took out in 1991 to help cover the costs of the Gulf war, bankers said
yesterday, Reuter reports from Dubai. They said the payment was due on
November 21 or 22, the third of five quarterly instalments of Dollars 900m
each.
